  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Game Story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On a small recreational island in the South Pacific, a sphere appears that should not exist. The SCP Foundation sends you to search for missing persons and direct the removal of SCP.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras/8983b14cbb439bc2daaa84cb2f866162.avif?t=1751986267\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras_big/8983b14cbb439bc2daaa84cb2f866162.avif?t=1751986267 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Game System</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon Upgrade, Armor Upgrade</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It can be destroyed when you strengthen the equipment, but with talisman, you can create a 100% success rate</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras/6f001b2f3232409da1d89f1178b6fd25.avif?t=1751986267\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras_big/6f001b2f3232409da1d89f1178b6fd25.avif?t=1751986267 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character Skill</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the fun of fostering characters with the points earned when attacking the enemy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras/c518adae330015a265a6583b7399096b.avif?t=1751986267\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras_big/c518adae330015a265a6583b7399096b.avif?t=1751986267 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follower</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colleagues are very powerful, and they cost a lot of money to hire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras/1edae72a19a8e29a26dd7c87e0cafd7b.avif?t=1751986267\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras_big/1edae72a19a8e29a26dd7c87e0cafd7b.avif?t=1751986267 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon Parts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equipped with parts increases the performance of the weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras/abb2d558ec0d221229e30e0a344eda85.avif?t=1751986267\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras_big/abb2d558ec0d221229e30e0a344eda85.avif?t=1751986267 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buff</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can receive up to four beneficial buffs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras/f3fe8b825b698682cedcf35814c2adc4.avif?t=1751986267\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras_big/f3fe8b825b698682cedcf35814c2adc4.avif?t=1751986267 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sleeping</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't have a recovery kit, try to recover your stamina by sleeping.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras/7cf40e16c4698cd3abc9b5281ac76c05.avif?t=1751986267\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras_big/7cf40e16c4698cd3abc9b5281ac76c05.avif?t=1751986267 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TV</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can watch personal videos on TV, but if the video memory is low, the probability of crash increases</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras/39b8a329bc47c632bd82356b85f28446.avif?t=1751986267\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras_big/39b8a329bc47c632bd82356b85f28446.avif?t=1751986267 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mutant</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Regular monsters have a chance of mutating, and the probability increases over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras/53f1d7cf29dc5e3697f576631387ff3f.avif?t=1751986267\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3287730/extras_big/53f1d7cf29dc5e3697f576631387ff3f.avif?t=1751986267 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DLSS3, FSR3</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the Options pane, you can select the Frame Booster option.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lumen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can increase performance by turning lumen none in the graphics options.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >different normal enemy depend on time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Normal monsters get stronger as time goes by.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. My first game, solo dev.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's my first game I'm developing by myself, so there are many problems. If you watch me with a generous heart, I'll do my best to fix the problems and complete the game.</p>",
